Author: ICOtimeline
Title: [BOUNTY] [ICO] WHIZZ Coin | The future of crypto investments and payments
Body: More Information About Whizz Coin ICO https://icotimeline.com/whizz-coin/  https://i.imgur.com/G5Vwswi.png  Welcome to the bounty campaign of Whizz Coin where  1.6875 million WHZ tokens worth 2812.5 ETH will be disbursed!!!!  https://i.imgur.com/Y7NvBAX.png  Eligibility 1. Have at least 200 followers and make privacy settings open for your page 2. Only one Facebook account per person is allowed 3. Facebook account must have at least 70% real followers  Register 1. Like and follow the Whizz coin official Facebook page 2. Register your participation below      Participate Here  Rules 1. You will be considered a Normal Activity user if you like and share 4 Whizz coin posts per week 2. You will be considered a Good Activity user if you like and share 4 Whizz coin posts per week, and make 2 posts about Whizz coin per week 3.The post should  contain a link  to the official website and hashtag #whizzcoin 4.Posts must be in English 5. Valid posts should contain 100 words or more 6.
